            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Hi,<br>
            <br>
            I have 2 Immediate requirements opening for a <font color="#800000"><strong>Sr. Unix Admin // </strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: maroon; font-size: 14pt"><strong>Windows Admin</strong> <font color="#3366ff"><font size="3">positions in</font><strong> </strong></font><font color="#3366ff"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">Columbus</span><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">, OH</span></font></span></font></font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Please send me word formatted resume with 2 professional references to </font><a href="mailto:kali@xperttech.com" title="blocked::mailto:kali@xperttech.com"><span style="color: #3366ff"><span title="blocked::mailto:kali@xperttech.com"><strong><font size="5">kali@xperttech.com</font></strong></span></span></a><font size="3">&nbsp; </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri; color: black"><font size="3">Position 1:</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: maroon; font-size: 14pt"><font size="3">Position: Sr. Unix Admin</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">Location: </span></strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">Columbus</span><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">, OH</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">Duration: </span></strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">6 months - might extend</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">Job Description</span></strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">:</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><strong><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">Interview Process:</span></strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">&nbsp; Phone Screen to Onsite interview - MUST be able to interview in person</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Must haves:</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">AIX 5.3 or 6.1</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">RedHat Enterprise</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">EXCELLENT communication skills - someone that can execute goals, give updates in status meetings, lead team on project work</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">***This role is NOT day to day administration, rather working on project work***</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Job Description:</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">The candidate must have skills in performing <strong>UNIX administration</strong> on RedHat Enterprise Linux 4, 5 and AIX 5.3 or 6.1. The ideal candidate will also have skills in application development and support on Solaris 9 or above.&nbsp; The UNIX administrator will be responsible for administering several servers (RedHat &amp; AIX) in the company supporting critical applications/systems. Primary responsibilities include administration of user account profiles, system backup and recovery processes, troubleshooting operating system issues, system software and hardware installations, application installation/maintenance support and system monitoring.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri; color: black"><font size="3">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri; color: black"><font size="3">Position 2:</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: maroon; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: normal">Position: </span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: maroon; font-size: 14pt">Windows Admin </span></strong></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">Location: </span></strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">Columbus</span><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">, OH</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">Duration: </span></strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">6 months - might extend</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">Interview Process:</span></strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">&nbsp; Phone Screen to Onsite interview - MUST be able to interview in person</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Must haves: </font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><u><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt">Either</span></u><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"> Exchange experience OR SCCM/SCOM&nbsp;experience - MUST have one of these PowerShell, BlackBerry Enterprise Server (BES)</span></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Job Description:</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3366ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">The candidate must have skills in performing <strong>Microsoft Windows administration</strong> on Enterprise server 2003 and 2008 including 64bit. The ideal candidate will also have skills in application development and support of Microsoft enterprise products such as Exchange, Active Directory, System Center including Operations Manager and Configuration Manager.&nbsp; The Microsoft administrator will be responsible for administering hundreds of servers in the company supporting critical applications/systems running as physical or virtual machines within ESX (VMware). Primary responsibilities include administration of user account profiles, system backup and recovery processes, troubleshooting operating system issues, system software and hardware installations, application installation/maintenance support and system monitoring.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Kali Venkat</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: green; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">XpertTech Inc</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">400 W Cummings Park,</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Suite#5450A</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Woburn, MA-01801</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt">Email: </span><span style="font-family: 'Sans Serif'; font-size: 9pt"><a href="mailto:kali@xperttech.com" title="blocked::mailto:kali@xperttech.com"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><span title="blocked::mailto:kali@xperttech.com">kali@xperttech.com</span></span></a></span>&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Phone: 781-926-0782</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Fax: 781-207-0709</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -qt-block-indent: 0; -qt-user-state: 0"><span style="font-family: 'Sans Serif'; font-size: 9pt"><a href="http://www.xperttech.com/" title="blocked::http://www.xperttech.com/"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: #3333ff; font-size: 11pt"><span title="blocked::http://www.xperttech.com/"><font size="3">www.xperttech.com</font></span></span></a><font size="3"> </font></span></div>
